        Model representing a shipping method in the Android SDK.

        label - Human friendly label specifying the shipping method that can be shown in the UI.
        identifier - Identifier for the shipping method.
        amount - The cost in minor unit based on currency
        currency - The currency that the specified amount will be rendered in.
        detail - Human friendly information such as estimated shipping times that can be shown inthe UI
